1
00:01:32,130 --> 00:01:34,990
[How dare you!?]

2
00:01:35,030 --> 00:01:38,030
[Episode 19]

3
00:02:01,310 --> 00:02:02,240
What does it say?

4
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:05,100
It's Yan language.

5
00:02:06,790 --> 00:02:09,190
The Emperor
is going to Mount Bei tomorrow.

6
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:11,840
Someone wants to kill you.

7
00:02:12,750 --> 00:02:15,210
You can leave the city
through the west gate.

8
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:17,160
Could our identities

9
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:18,300
have been exposed?

10
00:02:19,450 --> 00:02:22,110
Does he know
we're planning to kill the Emperor?

11
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:27,090
That's impossible.

12
00:02:27,470 --> 00:02:28,670
If that were the case,

13
00:02:29,829 --> 00:02:30,840
how could we still be

14
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:32,450
safe here at the posthouse?

15
00:02:33,630 --> 00:02:34,430
Could there be

16
00:02:35,430 --> 00:02:37,560
other compatriots hiding in the city,

17
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:39,030
quietly aiding us?

18
00:02:39,560 --> 00:02:41,870
Or is this some kind of trap?

19
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:56,560
[Capital of Xia]

20
00:03:06,810 --> 00:03:10,550
[Zhao Wucheng,
Commander of the Imperial Guards]

21
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:30,810
Hurry up!

22
00:03:31,190 --> 00:03:31,650
Keep up!

23
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:33,660
Hurry!

24
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:40,300
They withdrew many Imperial Guards.

25
00:03:40,470 --> 00:03:41,600
The Imperial Guards

26
00:03:41,870 --> 00:03:43,870
are the Emperor's personal troops.

27
00:03:45,079 --> 00:03:47,310
Pulling out so many at once?

28
00:03:48,750 --> 00:03:49,610
Could it be that

29
00:03:50,200 --> 00:03:52,260
Xiahou Dan really went to Mount Bei?

30
00:03:52,750 --> 00:03:53,960
Then aside from the Emperor,

31
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:55,490
who else would want us dead?

32
00:03:57,190 --> 00:03:59,120
The people of Great Xia are treacherous.

33
00:03:59,120 --> 00:04:00,450
We don't know if the note

34
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:02,120
is true or false.

35
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:12,200
Let's wait a bit longer.

36
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:30,390
Stop the carriage!

37
00:04:30,390 --> 00:04:30,920
Stop!

38
00:04:34,430 --> 00:04:34,920
Well...

39
00:04:37,830 --> 00:04:39,230
My Lord, are you alright?

40
00:04:41,680 --> 00:04:42,210
I'm fine.

41
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:47,690
Did...

42
00:04:48,730 --> 00:04:49,680
Did something

43
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:50,680
just rush past?

44
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:51,680
Did it?

45
00:04:52,390 --> 00:04:53,650
I didn't see anything.

46
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:54,810
This forest is huge.

47
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,730
It was probably a small animal.

48
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:58,090
Alright.

49
00:04:58,720 --> 00:04:59,250
Let's go.

50
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:01,360
Steady the carriage.

51
00:05:01,430 --> 00:05:01,750
Yes.

52
00:05:10,490 --> 00:05:11,020
Let's go.

53
00:05:18,040 --> 00:05:18,830
Your Highness,

54
00:05:18,830 --> 00:05:19,560
at Mount Bei,

55
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:22,000
Lord Cao has already made arrangements
with his men.

56
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:25,260
As for Lord Mu, he's on his way
to the posthouse with his men.

57
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:27,120
Thank you.

58
00:05:28,070 --> 00:05:28,800
Please, sit.

59
00:05:35,630 --> 00:05:36,120
Stop.

60
00:05:55,980 --> 00:05:56,440
My Lord,

61
00:05:56,710 --> 00:05:58,240
they have all left the city.

62
00:05:58,430 --> 00:05:59,340
Great.

63
00:06:00,750 --> 00:06:01,640
Remember,

64
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:03,870
make a big scene later.

65
00:06:04,540 --> 00:06:05,240
Do you understand?

66
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:05,560
Yes.

67
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:08,680
Once it's done,

68
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:11,190
Her Majesty will reward you generously.

69
00:06:11,190 --> 00:06:12,120
I should thank Her Majesty.

70
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:13,180
Thank you, My Lord.

71
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:20,480
Move!

72
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:22,280
Move!

73
00:06:27,230 --> 00:06:31,020
[Yixuan Inn]

74
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,950
Hurry up and get out of the way!

75
00:06:29,950 --> 00:06:31,240
By order of the Empress Dowager.

76
00:06:31,240 --> 00:06:32,950
The envoy delegation
has violated the laws of Great Xia

77
00:06:32,950 --> 00:06:34,480
and endangered the safety of its people.

78
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:36,390
They are to be arrested immediately!

79
00:06:36,390 --> 00:06:37,350
On His Majesty's command, we're here...

80
00:06:37,350 --> 00:06:38,240
Anyone who resists

81
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:39,840
will be executed on the spot!

82
00:06:48,430 --> 00:06:49,760
The letter was right.

83
00:06:50,070 --> 00:06:51,470
Someone wants to kill us.

84
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:53,960
The Emperor's soldiers are fighting them.

85
00:06:54,159 --> 00:06:55,020
Your Highness,

86
00:06:55,159 --> 00:06:57,020
should we charge out in the chaos?

87
00:06:57,800 --> 00:06:59,000
How many of them are here?

88
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,030
Several dozen.

89
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:09,850
The people of Great Xia
truly underestimated us.

90
00:07:10,190 --> 00:07:11,520
They think these few men

91
00:07:11,720 --> 00:07:13,310
are enough to kill us all.

92
00:07:15,270 --> 00:07:15,800
It's hot.

93
00:07:17,270 --> 00:07:18,530
Let it cool down first.

94
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:20,260
Once we deal with them,

95
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:22,920
we'll come back and drink it slowly.

96
00:07:27,780 --> 00:07:29,290
[Yixuan Inn]

97
00:07:30,230 --> 00:07:30,520
[Yixuan Inn]

98
00:07:31,020 --> 00:07:31,540
[Yixuan Inn]

99
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:12,910
[Yixuan Inn]

100
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:21,620
Lord Wu.

101
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:28,020
Your Highness.

102
00:08:31,020 --> 00:08:33,020
[Tu'er has extraordinary combat skills]

103
00:08:33,020 --> 00:08:35,030
[Most of the assassins were killed or
injured. The plan went smoothly]

104
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:36,669
Excellent.

105
00:08:38,330 --> 00:08:41,590
He truly deserves his title
as the top fighter in Yan State.

106
00:08:44,570 --> 00:08:52,240
[Yixuan Inn]

107
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:55,800
Sir, your martial skill is formidable.

108
00:08:56,030 --> 00:08:56,630
Thank you.

109
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:00,730
Satisfying!

110
00:09:01,030 --> 00:09:02,590
We killed so many people of Great Xia.

111
00:09:02,590 --> 00:09:05,990
Let's see how that old
Emperor of Yan can still talk peace now.

112
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:07,630
Yan delegation?

113
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:18,860
Your Highness,

114
00:09:18,980 --> 00:09:20,240
what should we do next?

115
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:24,780
Change into their clothes

116
00:09:25,370 --> 00:09:26,700
and take their weapons.

117
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:28,690
We

118
00:09:30,550 --> 00:09:31,810
are going to Mount Bei!

119
00:09:38,550 --> 00:09:40,350
A light rain comes from the east,

120
00:09:41,320 --> 00:09:43,100
carried by a fair wind.

121
00:09:46,150 --> 00:09:47,390
It seems this rain

122
00:09:48,390 --> 00:09:50,360
is inevitable.

123
00:09:50,930 --> 00:09:53,950
[Capital of Xia]

124
00:09:58,480 --> 00:09:59,160
Who are you?

125
00:09:59,640 --> 00:10:02,290
[Token]

126
00:10:00,080 --> 00:10:01,320
We are acting under orders

127
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:02,320
to leave the city.

128
00:10:10,290 --> 00:10:10,820
Make way.

129
00:10:11,940 --> 00:10:12,840
[Token]

130
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:12,880
Let them pass.

131
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:28,100
Lord Zhao.

132
00:10:28,510 --> 00:10:29,310
I have already

133
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:30,410
let those people

134
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:31,960
out of the city.

135
00:10:37,750 --> 00:10:39,210
Who are you talking about?

136
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:40,700
My Lord,

137
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:42,850
I followed your order and...

138
00:10:44,870 --> 00:10:46,840
I only gave one order today.

139
00:10:47,270 --> 00:10:49,750
That was to guard the gate as usual.

140
00:10:50,630 --> 00:10:51,430
Do you hear me?

141
00:10:52,360 --> 00:10:52,720
Yes.

142
00:11:12,340 --> 00:11:13,940
Watch the situation closely

143
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:16,060
and report any developments at once.

144
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:19,910
My Lord, are you worried...

145
00:11:23,480 --> 00:11:25,740
You never put all your eggs in one basket.

146
00:11:27,910 --> 00:11:29,390
Only Heaven knows

147
00:11:31,730 --> 00:11:33,990
whether today we'll save the Emperor...

148
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:37,450
or be too late.

149
00:11:53,750 --> 00:11:55,960
A ceasefire and trade
between Yan and Great Xia

150
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:57,390
does Prince Duan no harm.

151
00:11:58,360 --> 00:11:59,480
No matter how you look at it,

152
00:11:59,480 --> 00:12:01,940
he has no reason
to sabotage the peace talks.

153
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:04,960
So what detail have I missed?

154
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:07,200
Your Highness, don't worry.

155
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:08,750
His Majesty said if there's an emergency,

156
00:12:08,750 --> 00:12:10,550
he will send someone to tell you.

157
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:12,320
Has Consort Xie
shown any unusual behavior?

158
00:12:12,320 --> 00:12:14,380
Consort Xie has been in her courtyard

159
00:12:14,790 --> 00:12:15,670
all morning.

160
00:12:41,910 --> 00:12:44,670
She's been burning paper offerings
for her unborn child.

161
00:12:44,670 --> 00:12:46,470
She's burning them very slowly.

162
00:12:46,510 --> 00:12:48,440
It's more like she's toasting them

163
00:12:48,910 --> 00:12:49,970
than burning them.

164
00:12:52,390 --> 00:12:54,120
Roasting them... with fire?

165
00:12:59,120 --> 00:13:02,610
[All is as usual.
Prince Duan advocates peace talks]

166
00:13:01,200 --> 00:13:01,630
Yes.

167
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:03,480
How could I forget?

168
00:13:02,610 --> 00:13:06,400
[I'm being watched]

169
00:13:04,080 --> 00:13:06,880
Xie Yong'er used this trick
in the original story.

170
00:13:12,120 --> 00:13:14,170
[I'm being watched.
His Majesty is in danger at Mount Bei]

171
00:13:12,630 --> 00:13:13,690
I'm being watched.

172
00:13:14,170 --> 00:13:16,230
[The Yan people
are attempting an assassination]

173
00:13:14,360 --> 00:13:15,670
His Majesty is in danger at Mount Bei.

174
00:13:15,670 --> 00:13:18,400
The Yan people
are attempting an assassination.

175
00:13:30,360 --> 00:13:34,910
[Kunyu Palace]

176
00:13:31,910 --> 00:13:32,960
Consort Xie,

177
00:13:33,510 --> 00:13:35,320
you haven't fully recovered yet.

178
00:13:35,320 --> 00:13:37,600
His Highness has repeatedly instructed us.

179
00:13:37,600 --> 00:13:39,860
You should return inside and rest early.

180
00:13:42,510 --> 00:13:44,270
You've been doing this all morning.

181
00:13:44,270 --> 00:13:45,730
At a time like this,

182
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:48,400
please don't make things difficult for me.

183
00:13:58,700 --> 00:14:00,220
[Token]

184
00:14:04,960 --> 00:14:06,030
Thank you, Eunuch.

185
00:14:08,150 --> 00:14:09,440
Then I'll trouble you

186
00:14:09,590 --> 00:14:10,910
to help me

187
00:14:10,910 --> 00:14:12,170
clean these things up.

188
00:14:13,650 --> 00:14:21,970
[Kunyu Palace]

189
00:14:13,870 --> 00:14:15,320
Ling, let's go back inside.

190
00:14:15,320 --> 00:14:15,670
Yes.

191
00:14:25,030 --> 00:14:26,960
Your Highness, what's wrong with you?

192
00:14:26,960 --> 00:14:28,770
Wake up! Your Highness!

193
00:14:29,240 --> 00:14:30,100
Your Highness!

194
00:14:50,290 --> 00:14:52,510
[Token]

195
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:55,390
Your Highness,
word has come from the city.

196
00:14:55,390 --> 00:14:56,320
The Yan people killed the guards

197
00:14:56,320 --> 00:14:58,520
and their whereabouts are now unknown.

198
00:15:01,530 --> 00:15:03,120
Prepare a secret guard outfit for me.

199
00:15:03,120 --> 00:15:04,120
We're leaving the city.

200
00:15:04,120 --> 00:15:05,250
Why, Your Highness?

201
00:15:05,270 --> 00:15:07,000
The Yan people are heading to Mount Bei
to assassinate His Majesty.

202
00:15:07,000 --> 00:15:09,080
Prince Duan's men
are secretly aiding them.

203
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:10,270
We're going to save His Majesty.

204
00:15:10,270 --> 00:15:11,130
Your Highness,

205
00:15:11,150 --> 00:15:12,080
His Majesty told us

206
00:15:12,080 --> 00:15:13,000
that if there is any danger,

207
00:15:13,000 --> 00:15:13,870
we are to protect you

208
00:15:13,870 --> 00:15:15,320
and ensure you do not leave the palace.

209
00:15:15,320 --> 00:15:17,080
The mountain must be crawling
with Prince Duan's men.

210
00:15:17,080 --> 00:15:18,750
Besides, you don't know martial arts.

211
00:15:18,750 --> 00:15:20,950
Even if you go there, it would be in vain.

212
00:15:22,720 --> 00:15:24,850
Can you mobilize the Imperial Guards?

213
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:25,960
Only Prince Duan can do it.

214
00:15:25,960 --> 00:15:27,220
That's what I thought.

215
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:29,240
Zhao Wucheng,
Commander of the Imperial Guards,

216
00:15:29,240 --> 00:15:30,910
has already been bought over
by Prince Duan.

217
00:15:30,910 --> 00:15:32,170
If we report it rashly,

218
00:15:32,320 --> 00:15:33,580
it will only alert him.

219
00:15:33,750 --> 00:15:35,150
There's no time to worry about that now.

220
00:15:35,150 --> 00:15:36,680
Bring out what we prepared.

221
00:15:39,370 --> 00:15:40,230
Your Highness,

222
00:15:40,320 --> 00:15:41,450
Consort Xie sent someone to deliver this.

223
00:15:40,770 --> 00:15:44,950
[Token]

224
00:15:45,600 --> 00:15:46,380
Xie Yong'er?

225
00:15:47,340 --> 00:15:48,100
That's it.

226
00:15:48,700 --> 00:15:50,200
You stay in the palace
and protect Consort Xie.

227
00:15:50,200 --> 00:15:51,800
The rest of you, come with me.

228
00:16:32,080 --> 00:16:34,880
The surroundings here
are indeed quite pleasant.

229
00:16:35,480 --> 00:16:37,080
I am glad you like it, Mother.

230
00:16:38,390 --> 00:16:39,630
Heaven bestows
the Five Virtues upon our people,

231
00:16:39,630 --> 00:16:41,750
including a mother's kindness
and a son's filial devotion.

232
00:16:41,750 --> 00:16:44,150
Now that the rain falls
to bless all things,

233
00:16:44,150 --> 00:16:46,180
it is all thanks to Your Majesties.

234
00:16:49,490 --> 00:16:50,610
Walk with me.

235
00:17:22,680 --> 00:17:23,609
Are you alright?

236
00:17:26,190 --> 00:17:28,390
There are soldiers hiding in the woods.

237
00:17:28,530 --> 00:17:31,460
They were already there
when we went up the mountain.

238
00:17:31,480 --> 00:17:33,880
It's a good thing
Wanyin didn't come along.

239
00:17:34,000 --> 00:17:35,330
Did you bring the thing?

240
00:17:47,590 --> 00:17:49,550
What lovely weather.

241
00:18:01,030 --> 00:18:04,420
Son, you attend to countless affairs
and keep the realm in your heart.

242
00:18:04,260 --> 00:18:09,940
[Be Remembered with Honor for All Ages]

243
00:18:04,960 --> 00:18:06,290
Despite such busyness,

244
00:18:06,720 --> 00:18:10,070
you still took the time
to inspect my mausoleum with me.

245
00:18:10,790 --> 00:18:12,750
I'm deeply moved.

246
00:18:13,830 --> 00:18:14,650
Look.

247
00:18:15,030 --> 00:18:16,070
Mount Bei

248
00:18:16,830 --> 00:18:18,270
has pleasant scenery.

249
00:18:18,720 --> 00:18:21,350
This mausoleum is quite magnificent.

250
00:18:22,400 --> 00:18:23,160
Son,

251
00:18:23,790 --> 00:18:24,920
you are thoughtful.

252
00:18:25,480 --> 00:18:26,160
All of this

253
00:18:27,000 --> 00:18:28,550
is simply my duty.

254
00:18:32,510 --> 00:18:33,480
Indeed.

255
00:18:36,550 --> 00:18:37,640
My son

256
00:18:38,590 --> 00:18:40,110
lingers in the harem

257
00:18:40,790 --> 00:18:43,640
and busies himself
with the affairs of Great Xia.

258
00:18:44,550 --> 00:18:45,440
Now

259
00:18:46,110 --> 00:18:47,510
he even has to worry about

260
00:18:47,680 --> 00:18:49,080
matters of other states.

261
00:18:50,110 --> 00:18:51,860
Your duties truly

262
00:18:52,790 --> 00:18:54,720
are too many.

263
00:19:03,510 --> 00:19:06,110
I can't help but worry for you.

264
00:19:10,910 --> 00:19:14,500
[Be Remembered with Honor for All Ages]

265
00:19:11,590 --> 00:19:13,000
His Majesty's choice

266
00:19:13,270 --> 00:19:14,660
of Mount Bei as the site

267
00:19:14,960 --> 00:19:16,690
shows his remarkable insight.

268
00:19:17,200 --> 00:19:19,130
And with your abundant blessings,

269
00:19:19,430 --> 00:19:21,070
it is a perfect match.

270
00:19:21,540 --> 00:19:23,680
Such maternal kindness and filial devotion

271
00:19:23,680 --> 00:19:25,000
are a blessing

272
00:19:28,000 --> 00:19:29,460
to the people of Great Xia.

273
00:19:30,130 --> 00:19:34,890
[Be Remembered with Honor for All Ages]

274
00:19:30,310 --> 00:19:31,680
As long as my son is here,

275
00:19:32,590 --> 00:19:35,490
of course it is a blessing
to the people of Great Xia.

276
00:19:38,500 --> 00:19:39,500
It's just that...

277
00:19:42,310 --> 00:19:43,830
Now you've grown up,

278
00:19:44,590 --> 00:19:45,790
you have more and more

279
00:19:46,920 --> 00:19:48,510
ideas of your own.

280
00:19:49,610 --> 00:19:50,720
While

281
00:19:51,350 --> 00:19:53,110
I'm pleased,

282
00:19:53,680 --> 00:19:55,740
I'm actually more worried about you.

283
00:19:56,350 --> 00:19:57,030
Mother,

284
00:19:57,920 --> 00:19:59,000
why do you say that?

285
00:19:59,790 --> 00:20:00,810
Do you remember

286
00:20:01,750 --> 00:20:02,960
Shanyi, the dancer?

287
00:20:04,120 --> 00:20:06,180
The one who tried to assassinate you.

288
00:20:10,030 --> 00:20:10,670
Alright.

289
00:20:11,110 --> 00:20:12,440
Let's not talk about it.

290
00:20:13,200 --> 00:20:14,000
It's just that

291
00:20:15,110 --> 00:20:17,240
there's one thing I don't understand.

292
00:20:17,240 --> 00:20:18,350
Didn't that incident

293
00:20:18,350 --> 00:20:20,590
already teach you a lesson?

294
00:20:21,590 --> 00:20:24,000
Yet in what you've been doing
these past few days,

295
00:20:24,000 --> 00:20:26,530
I see signs of you
repeating the same mistake.

296
00:20:31,120 --> 00:20:32,170
Shanyi...

297
00:20:32,920 --> 00:20:35,580
was originally sent here
as a dancer to perform.

298
00:20:36,750 --> 00:20:38,010
Why did she stay

299
00:20:38,750 --> 00:20:40,150
and become my concubine?

300
00:20:40,960 --> 00:20:41,880
And why did she

301
00:20:42,880 --> 00:20:44,070
attempt to assassinate me
at the cost of her own life

302
00:20:44,070 --> 00:20:45,270
when she knew

303
00:20:46,720 --> 00:20:48,050
it could never succeed?

304
00:20:49,510 --> 00:20:50,770
Others might not know,

305
00:20:51,640 --> 00:20:52,300
but Mother,

306
00:20:54,070 --> 00:20:55,030
don't you know?

307
00:20:56,220 --> 00:20:57,480
What are you implying?

308
00:20:58,000 --> 00:20:59,350
What I mean is that

309
00:21:01,000 --> 00:21:02,530
a ceasefire and peace talks

310
00:21:02,900 --> 00:21:05,250
benefit the people of Great Xia.

311
00:21:06,000 --> 00:21:06,830
Why are you

312
00:21:07,550 --> 00:21:08,950
so unwilling to allow it?

313
00:21:17,160 --> 00:21:18,400
Yan State

314
00:21:19,190 --> 00:21:21,120
lies in a harsh and barbarous land.

315
00:21:21,720 --> 00:21:22,240
They are

316
00:21:22,720 --> 00:21:24,100
bloodthirsty

317
00:21:24,310 --> 00:21:25,500
and incorrigible.

318
00:21:25,920 --> 00:21:26,980
You saw it yourself

319
00:21:27,270 --> 00:21:28,920
at the Grand Longevity Banquet.

320
00:21:28,920 --> 00:21:31,400
Their greedy eyes and wild ambitions

321
00:21:31,400 --> 00:21:32,800
were clear for all to see.

322
00:21:34,400 --> 00:21:34,920
Son,

323
00:21:35,750 --> 00:21:37,400
surely you saw that too.

324
00:21:40,160 --> 00:21:40,830
Thank you

325
00:21:42,000 --> 00:21:43,460
for your concern, Mother.

326
00:21:44,290 --> 00:21:50,990
[Be Remembered with Honor for All Ages]

327
00:21:44,750 --> 00:21:45,590
Forget it.

328
00:21:47,240 --> 00:21:48,270
Let's say no more.

329
00:21:49,270 --> 00:21:51,070
There is no point in saying more.

330
00:21:51,310 --> 00:21:55,240
I only hope the young Crown Prince doesn't
take after your temperament

331
00:21:55,400 --> 00:21:57,120
and grow so stubborn.

332
00:22:00,070 --> 00:22:00,670
By the way,

333
00:22:01,640 --> 00:22:02,480
yesterday,

334
00:22:03,590 --> 00:22:06,400
the young Crown Prince
mentioned you to me.

335
00:22:06,770 --> 00:22:07,580
He said

336
00:22:07,750 --> 00:22:09,160
he missed his father.

337
00:22:10,790 --> 00:22:11,510
Go away!

338
00:22:12,200 --> 00:22:13,000
Your Majesty,

339
00:22:13,680 --> 00:22:16,010
this is a reward from the Empress Dowager.

340
00:22:17,830 --> 00:22:19,640
Whether Xiahou Dan cooperates or not...

341
00:22:19,640 --> 00:22:20,200
Don't come over!

342
00:22:20,200 --> 00:22:21,070
He must give me...

343
00:22:21,070 --> 00:22:21,440
Go away.

344
00:22:21,440 --> 00:22:22,920
A Crown Prince.

345
00:22:23,350 --> 00:22:25,210
Congratulations, Your Majesty.

346
00:22:26,240 --> 00:22:27,810
From this day on,

347
00:22:28,590 --> 00:22:30,790
he shall be the one and only Crown Prince

348
00:22:30,790 --> 00:22:32,740
of Great Xia.

349
00:22:33,350 --> 00:22:34,200
Yes.

350
00:22:37,270 --> 00:22:39,170
If you have some free time,

351
00:22:39,680 --> 00:22:40,830
go see him

352
00:22:41,830 --> 00:22:43,550
and check his studies.

353
00:22:44,640 --> 00:22:46,480
Things are unpredictable.

354
00:22:47,110 --> 00:22:48,790
If anything happens,

355
00:22:49,310 --> 00:22:50,680
the Crown Prince

356
00:22:51,440 --> 00:22:53,970
may have to take over the throne
temporarily.

357
00:22:54,070 --> 00:22:55,640
It's better to be prepared

358
00:22:56,100 --> 00:22:57,140
in advance.

359
00:23:04,310 --> 00:23:05,510
Why are you laughing?

360
00:23:08,310 --> 00:23:11,430
[Be Remembered with Honor for All Ages]

361
00:23:09,880 --> 00:23:11,300
Why are you laughing?

362
00:23:23,800 --> 00:23:25,000
Mother,

363
00:23:28,180 --> 00:23:29,930
did you suddenly say this today

364
00:23:34,400 --> 00:23:36,070
because you think

365
00:23:37,070 --> 00:23:38,310
he can now replace me

366
00:23:39,660 --> 00:23:41,310
as your new puppet?

367
00:23:43,840 --> 00:23:45,170
Are you out of your mind?

368
00:23:49,060 --> 00:23:50,470
You don't actually think

369
00:23:52,440 --> 00:23:55,500
I would develop any fatherly affection
for him, do you?

370
00:23:57,710 --> 00:23:58,890
What do you mean?

371
00:24:07,920 --> 00:24:09,850
Where is the Imperial Astronomer?

372
00:24:12,000 --> 00:24:12,830
I am here.

373
00:24:13,680 --> 00:24:15,110
Check the feng shui

374
00:24:16,230 --> 00:24:17,430
of the lower palaces,

375
00:24:18,510 --> 00:24:19,510
the sacred paths,

376
00:24:20,970 --> 00:24:23,020
and the stele pavilions nearby.

377
00:24:24,510 --> 00:24:25,440
Look carefully.

378
00:24:27,270 --> 00:24:28,730
There must be no mistakes.

379
00:24:31,750 --> 00:24:32,590
Y-Yes,

380
00:24:33,200 --> 00:24:34,000
Your Majesty.

381
00:24:41,830 --> 00:24:43,070
Did you intercept any news?

382
00:24:43,070 --> 00:24:43,910
Ma'am,

383
00:24:44,130 --> 00:24:46,160
we have been stationed here
for a long time,

384
00:24:46,160 --> 00:24:48,960
but no urgent messages
have arrived from the city.

385
00:24:50,020 --> 00:24:51,350
It's already this hour.

386
00:24:51,920 --> 00:24:53,720
Lord Mu should have acted by now.

387
00:24:54,440 --> 00:24:56,170
How could there be no movement?

388
00:25:27,240 --> 00:25:27,790
Guards!

389
00:25:43,240 --> 00:25:43,960
Kill!

390
00:25:49,790 --> 00:25:51,180
Why are they here?

391
00:25:51,590 --> 00:25:53,850
Didn't Mu Yun send men to intercept them?

392
00:26:14,920 --> 00:26:15,900
Assassins!

393
00:26:16,550 --> 00:26:18,610
Send the Imperial Guards for backup!

394
00:26:19,350 --> 00:26:20,520
Assassins!

395
00:26:21,350 --> 00:26:23,410
Send the Imperial Guards for backup!

396
00:26:33,610 --> 00:26:35,870
They... they're really killing people!

397
00:26:44,840 --> 00:26:46,570
I wonder if His Majesty is safe.

398
00:26:49,750 --> 00:26:51,070
His Majesty is in danger.

399
00:26:51,070 --> 00:26:51,930
As his subject,

400
00:26:53,390 --> 00:26:54,390
I must go save him.

401
00:26:54,790 --> 00:26:55,190
Right.

402
00:27:08,350 --> 00:27:10,740
What is this guy made of?

403
00:27:10,830 --> 00:27:12,580
Iron and steel?

404
00:27:13,000 --> 00:27:14,550
Judging by your fighting skill,

405
00:27:14,550 --> 00:27:17,550
you must be Tu'er,
the top fighter of Yan State, right?

406
00:27:17,750 --> 00:27:18,550
That's right.

407
00:27:19,330 --> 00:27:21,860
I'm here to take
the Great Xia Emperor's head!

408
00:27:22,960 --> 00:27:23,860
Who are you?

409
00:27:24,030 --> 00:27:25,810
I'm just an ordinary servant

410
00:27:25,880 --> 00:27:27,830
in the palace of Great Xia.

411
00:27:28,440 --> 00:27:30,440
You people of Great Xia are all talk!

412
00:27:30,920 --> 00:27:31,780
Bring it on!

413
00:27:32,750 --> 00:27:33,240
Come on.

414
00:27:50,510 --> 00:27:51,440
What's that?

415
00:27:51,480 --> 00:27:54,610
Nine Heavens Mystical Fire Repeating
Sleeve Crossbow!

416
00:27:57,310 --> 00:27:57,990
Today,

417
00:27:58,480 --> 00:27:59,350
either you die,

418
00:27:59,830 --> 00:28:00,800
or I do.

419
00:28:08,920 --> 00:28:10,210
And who are you?

420
00:28:10,690 --> 00:28:12,020
Mind your own business.

421
00:28:23,000 --> 00:28:24,130
Everyone, close in!

422
00:28:24,200 --> 00:28:24,940
He can't aim!

423
00:28:56,200 --> 00:28:58,270
Yeah, his aim's awful.

424
00:29:14,680 --> 00:29:16,050
Your Majesty, do it!

425
00:29:17,380 --> 00:29:18,510
Do it, Your Majesty!

426
00:29:18,830 --> 00:29:20,560
Your Majesty, watch your back!

427
00:29:23,160 --> 00:29:23,700
Dan.

428
00:29:28,100 --> 00:29:29,560
What is it, Your Highness?

429
00:29:29,880 --> 00:29:30,410
Nothing.

430
00:29:30,790 --> 00:29:31,520
Keep moving.

431
00:30:32,590 --> 00:30:32,920
Dan.

432
00:30:33,400 --> 00:30:34,060
How are you?

433
00:30:34,350 --> 00:30:34,940
Mr. Bei.

434
00:30:47,210 --> 00:30:47,650
Stop!

435
00:30:48,000 --> 00:30:48,880
Restricted royal grounds.

436
00:30:48,880 --> 00:30:50,210
No unauthorized entry!

437
00:30:56,680 --> 00:30:57,190
[Token]

438
00:30:57,640 --> 00:30:58,770
It's our own people.

439
00:30:59,290 --> 00:31:00,300
What are you doing here?

440
00:31:00,300 --> 00:31:03,920
[Token]

441
00:31:00,720 --> 00:31:02,120
His Highness assigned us

442
00:31:02,310 --> 00:31:03,590
to go up the mountain immediately.

443
00:31:03,590 --> 00:31:04,120
Make way.

444
00:31:05,310 --> 00:31:06,110
Let them pass.

445
00:31:15,110 --> 00:31:15,770
Over there!

446
00:31:43,280 --> 00:31:43,860
Mr. Yang?

447
00:31:44,680 --> 00:31:45,540
Your Highness?

448
00:31:45,920 --> 00:31:47,000
What are you doing here?

449
00:31:47,000 --> 00:31:48,000
It's a long story.

450
00:31:48,400 --> 00:31:49,310
How are things on your side?

451
00:31:49,310 --> 00:31:51,240
His Majesty is trapped at the mausoleum.

452
00:31:51,240 --> 00:31:51,810
The forest

453
00:31:51,810 --> 00:31:53,790
is filled with Prince Duan's ambushers.

454
00:31:53,790 --> 00:31:56,070
I tried to go down the mountain
to fetch the Imperial Guards,

455
00:31:56,070 --> 00:31:57,620
but was pursued by the ambushers.

456
00:31:57,620 --> 00:31:59,640
Thank you for saving me just now,
Your Highness.

457
00:31:59,640 --> 00:32:00,500
Your Highness!

458
00:32:01,960 --> 00:32:02,490
Bad news!

459
00:32:02,590 --> 00:32:03,920
Someone is catching up.

460
00:32:04,880 --> 00:32:05,510
Mr. Yang.

461
00:32:05,720 --> 00:32:06,920
Run east through the forest,

462
00:32:06,920 --> 00:32:07,920
then head down the mountain. Hurry!

463
00:32:07,920 --> 00:32:08,510
Your Highness,

464
00:32:08,510 --> 00:32:09,790
what... what about you?

465
00:32:09,790 --> 00:32:11,000
Don't worry, Mr. Yang.

466
00:32:11,000 --> 00:32:11,750
I have a plan.

467
00:32:13,780 --> 00:32:14,450
Mr. Yang.

468
00:32:15,160 --> 00:32:16,320
The safety of His Majesty

469
00:32:16,320 --> 00:32:17,400
and the future of Great Xia

470
00:32:17,400 --> 00:32:18,600
are entrusted to you.

471
00:32:19,070 --> 00:32:21,670
You must bring the Imperial Guards
to save him.

472
00:32:22,190 --> 00:32:22,640
I

473
00:32:23,660 --> 00:32:24,190
am going!

474
00:32:27,240 --> 00:32:27,900
Xiahou Dan.

475
00:32:28,630 --> 00:32:29,690
I'll be there soon.

476
00:32:30,400 --> 00:32:31,160
Hold on.

477
00:32:32,030 --> 00:32:32,690
I have to...

478
00:32:33,590 --> 00:32:34,580
hold on.

479
00:33:00,680 --> 00:33:01,760
There is someone

480
00:33:04,270 --> 00:33:05,670
waiting for me to go back.

481
00:33:11,660 --> 00:33:13,820
Zhang San's Diary.

482
00:34:51,590 --> 00:34:56,360
Long live the Emperor!

483
00:35:00,230 --> 00:35:01,400
You may rise.
